<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٨٦٤٦ - عَنِ ابْنِ عُيَيْنَةَ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الْحَسَنِ بْنِ عُبَيْدِ اللَّهِ النَّخَعِيِّ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ عَنْ جَنِينِ الْبَقَرَةِ؟<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«إِنَّمَا هُوَ رُكْنٌ مِنْ أَرْكَانِهَا»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>